Wicked Cantina Bradenton Beach - Paradise by the Bay Home Property About Us Experiences Home Property About Us Experiences Book Now Become a Host Places To Eat Wicked Cantina Bradenton Beach Nestled in the heart of Anna Maria Island, Wicked Cantina invites patrons to embark on a culinary journey blending Mexican flavors with Gulf Coast flair. Boasting a vibrant and energetic atmosphere, this restaurant is a favorite for those seeking bold and savory dishes. From flavorful tacos to sizzling fajitas, Wicked Cantina showcases a diverse menu that caters to a variety of tastes. The lively ambiance, paired with an extensive selection of tequilas and craft margaritas, creates a festive setting for friends and families to enjoy delicious meals while soaking in the island vibes.
